# Development Log Reminder

## Rule
ALWAYS update `development-log.md` after significant AI interactions, feature implementations, or architectural decisions.

## Requirements
- Include AI model name in each entry
- Brief description of what was done
- Key decisions made by AI
- List of files changed
- Context for next AI session
- Keep entries focused and concise

## Purpose
This is for AI context preservation between sessions, not detailed project documentation. Helps maintain continuity when switching between different AI assistants or sessions.

## Entry Format
Follow the format specified in `development-log.md` for consistency.
